<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Viveha | Portfolio</title>

<meta name="description" content="Personal Portfolio Website of Viveha showcasing skills, projects and achievements.">
<meta name="keywords" content="Portfolio, HTML5, Accessibility, Web Development, Student">
<meta name="author" content="Viveha">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

html{
    scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
    background:#f5f7fb;
    color:#333;
}

/* Header */
header{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4f46e5,#7c3aed);
    color:white;
    padding:20px 8%;
    position:sticky;
    top:0;
    z-index:1000;
}

nav{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
}

.logo{
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

nav ul{
    list-style:none;
    display:flex;
    gap:25px;
}

nav a{
    text-decoration:none;
    color:white;
    font-weight:600;
}

nav a:hover{
    color:#ffd700;
}

/* Hero */
.hero{
    min-height:90vh;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    background:linear-gradient(rgba(79,70,229,.9),
    rgba(124,58,237,.9));
    color:white;
    padding:30px;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:55px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.hero p{
    font-size:22px;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    background:white;
    color:#4f46e5;
    padding:12px 25px;
    border-radius:30px;
    text-decoration:none;
    font-weight:bold;
}

/* Sections */
section{
    padding:80px 10%;
}

.section-title{
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:40px;
    font-size:36px;
    color:#4f46e5;
}

/* About */
.about{
    text-align:center;
    max-width:900px;
    margin:auto;
    font-size:18px;
}

/* Cards */
.card-container{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:15px;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
    transition:.3s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.card h3{
    color:#4f46e5;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

/* Aside */
aside{
    margin-top:40px;
    background:#eef2ff;
    padding:20px;
    border-left:5px solid #4f46e5;
    border-radius:10px;
}

/* Contact */
form{
    max-width:600px;
    margin:auto;
    background:white;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:15px;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

label{
    display:block;
    margin-top:15px;
    font-weight:600;
}

input,
textarea{
    width:100%;
    padding:12px;
    margin-top:5px;
    border:1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius:8px;
}

button{
    margin-top:20px;
    width:100%;
    padding:12px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:8px;
    background:#4f46e5;
    color:white;
    font-size:16px;
    cursor:pointer;
}

button:hover{
    background:#3730a3;
}

/* Footer */
footer{
    background:#1e293b;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}

/* Skip Link */
.skip-link{
    position:absolute;
    left:-999px;
}

.skip-link:focus{
    left:10px;
    top:10px;
    background:yellow;
    padding:10px;
    color:black;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero h1{
    font-size:38px;
}

.hero p{
    font-size:18px;
}

nav{
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:15px;
}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">
Skip to Main Content
</a>

<header>
<nav aria-label="Main Navigation">

<div class="logo">Viveha</div>

<ul>
<li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
<li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
<li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
<li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
<li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
</ul>

</nav>
</header>

<main id="main-content">

<section class="hero" id="home">
<div>
<h1>Hello, I'm Viveha</h1>
<p>Student • Web Developer • AI Enthusiast</p>
<a href="#projects" class="btn">View Projects</a>
</div>
</section>

<section id="about">

<h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>

<article class="about">
<p>
I am a passionate student interested in Web Development,
Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning. I enjoy
creating responsive websites and learning modern
technologies that solve real-world problems.
</p>
</article>

<aside>
<h3>Quick Facts</h3>
<p>
✔ HTML5 & CSS3 <br>
✔ Python Programming <br>
✔ Machine Learning Enthusiast <br>
✔ Continuous Learner
</p>
</aside>

</section>

<section id="skills">

<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>

<div class="card-container">

<article class="card">
<h3>HTML5</h3>
<p>Semantic and accessible website development.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
<h3>CSS3</h3>
<p>Responsive and modern user interface design.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
<h3>JavaScript</h3>
<p>Interactive and dynamic web applications.</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
<h3>Python</h3>
<p>Programming, automation and machine learning.</p>
</article>

</div>

</section>

<section id="projects">

<h2 class="section-title">Projects</h2>

<div class="card-container">

<article class="card">
<h3>Portfolio Website</h3>
<p>
Developed a fully responsive portfolio website
using HTML5 and CSS3.
</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
<h3>Machine Learning Project</h3>
<p>
Built prediction models using Python and ML
algorithms.
</p>
</article>

<article class="card">
<h3>AI Chatbot</h3>
<p>
Designed a chatbot capable of basic interaction
and responses.
</p>
</article>

</div>

</section>

<section id="contact">

<h2 class="section-title">Contact Me</h2>

<form aria-label="Contact Form">

<label for="name">Full Name</label>
<input
type="text"
id="name"
name="name"
required>

<label for="email">Email Address</label>
<input
type="email"
id="email"
name="email"
required>

<label for="message">Message</label>
<textarea
id="message"
name="message"
rows="5"
required></textarea>

<button
type="submit"
aria-label="Send Message">
Send Message
</button>

</form>

</section>

</main>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Viveha Portfolio | Built with Semantic HTML5 & Accessibility Standards</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
